Package: openeR
Type: Package
Title: Document your scripts using standardized in-line comments
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Thomas Alcock
Maintainer: Thomas Alcock <thomas.alcock@statworx.com>
Description: openeR let's you document your (non-functional) scripts by inserting standardized
    doc strings into your script at the cursor position. The packages main function, openeR_gadget()
    should be used with an RStudio keyboard short cut. See the github README.md for more information.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    rstudioapi,
    shiny,
    miniUI
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
